column5: For all of you who wish to improve your fishing tech game, check out my buddy, FLW Pro, Josh Douglas as he presents another Navionics webinar, "Understanding Contour Lines and Mapping Features" Josh is a very knowledgeable and tech savvy angler, should be informative!  There is no charge for this webinar, here is the link to register - https://register.gotowebinar.com/register/5885708140932236813?source=eblast
I reposted that in a couple spots for ya...
Thanks TJ! Great times to learn!
Hey Dave, is the webinar on Youtube?  I am researching all electronics and mapping right now so when I go and get a new boat I will know what I want/need.  Thanks! Chrispy!
They usually have the webinar up on the Navionics YouTube Channel within a  week! It was very good, Josh knows his stuff! Keep checking, should be up soon!
Thanks so much Dave!!  Tight lines!  Chrispy!
